lead_paragraph: The United States starts its pursuit of a fourth straight gold medal in women's Olympic soccer over the next two weeks at the CONCACAF qualifying tournament in Texas.

headline.print_headline: US Women Start Quest for 4th Straight Olympic Gold Medal
